		    	<h4>BEST</h4>
		    	<p class="card-text">British Energy Saving Technology (BEST) specialise in the design, manufacture and development of a unique range of clean energy technologies. BEST’s flagship product, Eniscope, is a one-of-a-kind real-time energy management solution that harnesses the power of IoT, Big Data and AI to deliver Energy Savings, Measurement & Verification, Predictive Maintenance and Occupant Engagement. BEST deploys its solutions through a network of qualified partners operating in over 50 countries around the world and counts IBM, KFC, Nampak, Sheraton Hotels, 7-Eleven, Unisys and CBRE among its many end-users.</p>
		    	<hr />
		    	<h4>Partnership with Minimise</h4>
		    	<p class="card-text">BEST’s partnership with Minimise is unique and is founded on a simple, old-fashioned but actually timeless principle; trust. Inspired by Minimise’s revolutionary business model and its visionary leader, Daniel Badran, BEST took a leap of faith and followed Minimise into unknown waters. That faith was rewarded in the shape of Hillsborough County Public Schools (HCPS), one of, if not the, most advanced energy saving projects BEST has ever engaged with. BEST technologies are now the foundation of that project, providing the essential energy information tools that Minimise needs to deliver on its promises to HCPS to save energy, verify project performance, reduce maintenance costs and engage with staff and students.</p>
		    	<hr />
		    	<h4>Future as Minimise Partner</h4>
		    	<p class="card-text">BEST’s mission is to become the world leader in the delivery of real-time energy management and control technologies for multi-site operators. Partnering with Minimise makes that mission eminently more achievable. What’s more, the partnership is already uncovering new, innovative ways to save energy, which is driving BEST to design and develop new, innovative technologies to maximise on these opportunities. The energy efficiency industry is ripe for disruption and the Minimise/BEST partnership, augmented by Minimise’s other extraordinary partners, is perfectly placed to spearhead the revolution.</p>
